# .roadmap.novel_drugs

мһ‘м„ұ: 2026-05-07
кө¬лҸҷ: мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ directive "кё°мЎҙм—җ м—ҶлҠ” мӢ к·ң м•Ҫл¬ј ... м•Ҫл¬ј мқҙлҰ„ м•Ңм•„м„ң л§Ңл“Өкё° + мӢ к·ң м•Ҫл¬ј лӘ©лЎқ лЈЁнҠё л¬ём„ң н•ҳлӮҳм—җ м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠё"

ліё file мқҖ hexa-bio к°Җ мһҗмІҙ design н•ң мӢ к·ң м•Ҫл¬ј нӣ„ліҙ (de novo drug candidates) мқҳ лӢЁмқј root лӘ©лЎқ. кё°мЎҙ FDA м•Ҫл¬ј (H2O / aspirin / ibuprofen / paracetamol / caffeine / nirmatrelvir / pirfenidone / minoxidil-frag / vorinostat / finasteride / simvastatin) мҷҖ м§Ғкөҗ.

мқҙлҠ” hexa-bio Phase A-B-C мқҳ infrastructure кІҖмҰқ (cycles 78-107) кё°л°ҳ мң„мқҳ м§„м •н•ң лӢӨмқҢ лӢЁкі„ вҖ” VQE-guided de novo drug design мӢңлҸ„.

---

## 1. Naming convention

```
hxq-<disease-tag>-<target-tag>-<NNN>
```

| component       | values                                         |
|-----------------|------------------------------------------------|
| prefix          | `hxq-` (hexa-bio quantum)                      |
| disease-tag     | `ca` (cancer) / `al` (alopecia) / `mi` (myocardial) / `ln` (lung) / `gen` (general) / `cmt` (Charcot-Marie-Tooth) / `als` (amyotrophic lateral sclerosis) |
| target-tag      | abbreviated target identifier (3-4 letters)    |
| NNN             | 3-digit serial number per (disease, target)    |

Example:
- `hxq-ca-krs-001` = hexa-bio quantum, cancer, KRAS-G12C target, candidate #001
- `hxq-al-ar-001`  = alopecia, androgen receptor target
- `hxq-mi-hmg-001` = myocardial infarction, HMG-CoA reductase
- `hxq-ln-tgf-001` = lung normalization, TGF-ОІ receptor
- `hxq-gen-water-001` = generic / scaffold exploration
- `hxq-cmt-pmp22-001` = Charcot-Marie-Tooth, PMP22 3'UTR allele-selective siRNA target
- `hxq-als-hd6-001`   = ALS, HDAC6 inhibitor (CNS-penetrant variant вҖ” CMT л§җмҙҲ н•ңм • chemotype мҷҖ л¶„кё°)

