**Library snapshot post-Phase-B**: 16 drugs total (11 FDA + 5 novel) вҖ” 15 sub-ВөHa + 1 above-ВөHa (finasteride 1.020 ВөHa). hxq-gen-001 0.026 ВөHa = library best.

