## 5. Phase plan

### Phase A вҖ” Initial design land (cycle 108) вң“ COMPLETE
- 5 entry skeleton + naming convention
- SMILES specified (derivation лӘ…мӢң)

### Phase B вҖ” Build + VQE (cycle 111) вң“ COMPLETE вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ
- 5/5 novel drugs all sub-ВөHa
- hxq-gen-001 0.026 ВөHa = NEW LIBRARY BEST (paper-rounding limit territory)
- F-Q-6-B-real path universality кІҖмҰқ (FDA + de novo лӘЁл‘җ лҸҷмқј path)

### Phase C вҖ” Pocket supersystem (Tier 1 ramp F-Q-6-D) вҖ” IN-PROGRESS

#### Attempt 1: мһҗлҸҷ frontier-orbital ActiveSpaceTransformer (cycle 113) вҖ” honest-fail
- methyl_acrylate (Michael acceptor) + methyl_thiol (Cys mimic) supersystem
- мһҗлҸҷ 2e/2o ActiveSpaceTransformer к°Җ fragment HOMO+LUMO мҷҖ supersystem HOMO+LUMO м—җ лӢӨлҘё orbital mapping
- E_int = E(super) вҲ’ E(acrylate) вҲ’ E(thiol) = +5308 kcal/mol (physically nonsensical, wrong sign + magnitude)
- м§„лӢЁ: apples-to-oranges 2e/2o л№„көҗ вҖ” interaction energy кі„мӮ° invalid

#### Attempt 2: 4e/4o UCCSD on supersystem (cycle 113-114) вҖ” IN-PROGRESS
