| `hxq-cmt-sar1-alt-B`        | pyrido[2,3-d]pyrimidin-4(3H)-one     | C13H10FN5O    | 20    | 0.96 | 86.69 | 2        | -932.599178     | **0.26** вӯҗ       | вң… PASS   | sub-ВөHa, IP novel |
