н•өмӢ¬:
- вӯҗ **3 scaffold class TBD н•ҙмҶҢ** вҖ” gjb1-001-A (chemical chaperone) + kif5a-001-A (ATPase pocket pyrimidine) + tbk1-001-F (indole-pyridyl kinase chaperone). 5 schematic мӨ‘ small-mol 3мў… лӘЁл‘җ BBB-PASS + chem-acc PASS.
- рҹ”¬ **library мӢ кё°лЎқ**: `tbk1-001-A` 2e/2o delta = **0.0004 ВөHa = 0.4 nano-Ha** (BBB FAIL мқҙм§Җл§Ң VQE pipeline м •нҷ•лҸ„ record). `gjb1-001-B` 0.003 ВөHa = 3 nano-Ha (2мң„).
- рҹ§Ә BBB мЎ°кұҙ (logP 2.5-3.5 + TPSA <90 + HBD <3) мқҙ sub-ВөHa мҷҖ trade-off вҖ” sub-ВөHa нӣ„ліҙ (tbk1-001-A / gjb1-001-B) лҠ” BBB л¶Җм Ғн•© лҳҗлҠ” лӢЁмҲң. drug-like + BBB-pass + chem-acc лҸҷмӢң л§ҢмЎұ = gjb1-001-A / kif5a-001-A / tbk1-001-F 3мў….
- рҹ©ә IT delivery (gjb1) лҠ” BBB л¬ҙкҙҖ вҖ” gjb1-001-A мқҳ logP 3.31 мқҖ IT н•ңм • dosing м Ғн•© (Schwann м„ нғқм„ұ wet-lab).
- вҡ пёҸ tbk1 LoF rescue chemistry = discovery-stage вҖ” wet-lab paralog IKKОө м„ нғқм„ұ вүҘ500x кІҖмҰқ + autophagy/STING off-target audit н•„мҲҳ.

